<p>I have a problem with mvc:resource,please take a look</p>  <pre><code>&lt;servlet&gt;     &lt;servlet-name&gt;main&lt;/servlet-name&gt;     &lt;servlet-class&gt;org.springframework.web.servlet.DispatcherServlet&lt;/servlet-class&gt; &lt;/servlet&gt; &lt;servlet-mapping&gt;     &lt;servlet-name&gt;main&lt;/servlet-name&gt;     &lt;url-pattern&gt;/app/*&lt;/url-pattern&gt; &lt;/servlet-mapping&gt;  &lt;mvc:annotation-driven/&gt; &lt;mvc:resources mapping="/app/css/**" location="/WEB-INF/css/"/&gt;  &lt;link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="&lt;c:url value="/app/css/main.css" /&gt;"&gt; </code></pre>  <p>And how can you see css styles not going to be find. Here is project structure </p>  <p><a href="http://i.stack.imgur.com/qx0l8.png" rel="nofollow"><img src="http://i.stack.imgur.com/qx0l8.png" alt="enter image description here"></a></p>